Tk::ImageButton version 1.0
---------------------------

This provides the programmer a customizable/graphical
button that gives a user interface a more professional
look.

INSTALLATION

To install this widget, type the following

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

If that doesn't work then just copy the:

  ImageButton.pm
  ImageButton.pod

files into your site_lib/Tk directory.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the following widgets:

  Tk and Tk::Label

EXAMPLES

In the distribution there is a directory called "example", in here you will find
the files:

  ib_test.pl
  quit_clicked.bmp
  quit_disabled.bmp
  quit_normal.bmp
  quit_over.bmp

Run the file "ib_test.pl" with Perl for a demonstration of a multi-image button. View the file
"ib_test.pl" for an example of how to use the widget in your own scripts.

